import React from "react";
import Home from "../../Asset/Icons/Home";
import {
  Accordion,
  AccordionButton,
  AccordionIcon,
  AccordionItem,
  AccordionPanel,
  Box,
  HStack,
  Icon,
  Path,
  Text,
} from "native-base";
import Copy from "../../Asset/Icons/Copy";

export default function SidebarItems() {
  return (
    <Box mt={10}>
      <Accordion>
        <AccordionItem>
          <AccordionButton _expanded={{ backgroundColor: "orange.3" }}>
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Home color="#5F72E4" />
              <Text pt={1} fontWeight={500} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Dashboards
              </Text>
            </HStack>
            <AccordionIcon />
          </AccordionButton>
          <AccordionPanel>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
            eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim
            ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
            aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </AccordionPanel>
        </AccordionItem>

        {/* new accordian */}
        <AccordionItem>
          <AccordionButton _expanded={{ backgroundColor: "orange.3" }}>
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Copy color="#FB6440" />
              <Text px={1} fontWeight={500} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Examples
              </Text>
            </HStack>
            <AccordionIcon />
          </AccordionButton>
          <AccordionPanel>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
            eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim
            ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
            aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </AccordionPanel>
        </AccordionItem>
      </Accordion>
    </Box>
  );
}
